episodes.title: Jonestown Massacre, explained.
episodes.description:
The single largest deliberate loss of American life happened over 3,000 miles away from the closest American border; in a remote jungle in Guyana where the cult leader Jim Jones and the Peoples Temple, committed the biggest mass suicide in recent history.

01:01 - New Beginnings
06:41 - Signs of Trouble
08:45 - Jonestown
14:55 - Calm Before the Storm
24:24 - Revolutionary [Murder] Suicide

38:30 - Aftermath
